{"tid":1663544,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"星期一要返廣州","createTime":"2019-10-19T13:00:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-19T18:54:00.000Z","uid":165028,"like":1,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"f2b6a4328667af4f6c7f9d57162134c8b9fe8f11","tid":1663544,"uid":165028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T13:00:16.000Z","msg":"驚星期一高鐵站唔開<br />\n唔知聽日會唔會被破壞"},{"pid":"fb64cedf4fef6ff0784b57ba7c21d9ee8097f806","tid":1663544,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T13:00:55.000Z","msg":"[1020 行動Post] 香港人真係好痴線！不論組織力、耐力、創意玩到咁！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/eovgRS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/eovgRS</a>"},{"pid":"1588c396e813c441d0d4ffb649227ac52bc143d3","tid":1663544,"uid":249022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f2b6a4328667af4f6c7f9d57162134c8b9fe8f11","tid":1663544,"uid":165028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T13:00:16.000Z","msg":"驚星期一高鐵站唔開<br />\n唔知聽日會唔會被破壞"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T13:01:06.000Z","msg":"屌上去送死咩<br />\n冇必要唔好上去啦"},{"pid":"825c34ca04049eda8e8356f1852b15dc75648d32","tid":1663544,"uid":268123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T13:02:01.000Z","msg":"【香城施政報告2019】群策群力 轉危為機<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1656908\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1656908</a><br />\n<br />\n<em><strong>政治問題</strong></em><br />\n<br />\n- 重塑公民身分戶口政策保障國家、香港安全和利益<br />\n- 取消18區區議會、建立地域市政議會<br />\n- 禁止公務人員在任前、任內和任後獲港外榮典<br />\n- 改善高鐵一地兩檢操作方式<br />\n<br />\n<em><strong>便民基建</strong></em><br />\n<br />\n- 興建東鐵、西鐵快速線並完善輕鐵和西鐵聯乘關係<br />\n- 完善機場集體運輸並加強機場、港珠澳大橋協同發展<br />\n- 修正港鐵、巴士可加可減機制<br />\n<br />\n[i]<strong>醫療、教育方向</strong>[i]<br />\n<br />\n- 興建至少四所新區域全科醫院<br />\n- 以減少送院為目標的社區護理服務<br />\n- 重塑教育, 著重知識、技能層次分工<br />\n<br />\n求正評及幫推！"},{"pid":"646a9cd542f996cecc90bb6b40c59854f85ef72d","tid":1663544,"uid":230849,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T13:02:03.000